valueInfo: 0, I am sad once in a while. | 1, I am sad many times. | 2, I am sad all the time.
0, Nothing will ever work out for me. | 1, I am not sure if things will work out for me. | 2, Things will work out for me O.K.
0, I do most things O.K. | 1, I do many things wrong. | 2, I do everything wrong.
0, I have fun in many things. | 1, I have fun in some things. | 2, Nothing is fun at all.
0, I am important to my family. | 1, I am not sure if I am important to my family. | 2, My family is better off without me.
0, I hate myself. | 1, I do not like myself. | 2, I like myself.
0, All bad things are my fault. | 1, Many bad things are my fault. | 2, Bad things are usually not my fault.
0, I do not think about killing myself. | 1, I think about killing myself but would not do it. | 2, I want to kill myself.
0, I feel like crying every day. | 1, I feel like crying many days. | 2, I feel like crying once in a while.
0, I feel cranky all the time. | 1, I feel cranky many times. | 2, I am almost never cranky.
0, I feel like being with people. | 1, I do not like being with people many times. | 2, I do not want to be with people at all.
0, I cannot make up my mind about things. | 1, It is hard to make up my mind about things. | 2, I make up my mind about things easily.
0, I look O.K. | 1, There are some bad things about my looks. | 2, I look ugly.
0, I have to push myself all the time to do schoolwork. | 1, I have to push myself many times to do schoolwork. | 2, Doing schoolwork is not a big problem.
0, I have trouble sleeping every night. | 1, I have trouble sleeping many nights. | 2, I sleep pretty well.
0, I am tired once in a while. | 1, I am tired many days. | 2, I am tired all the time.
0, Most days I do not feel like eating. | 1, Many days I do not feel like eating. | 2, I eat pretty well.
0, I do not worry about aches and pains. | 1, I worry about aches and pains many times. | 2, I worry about aches and pains all the time.
0, I do not feel alone. | 1, I feel alone many times. | 2, I feel alone all the time.
0, I never have fun at school. | 1, I have fun at school only once in a while. | 2, I have fun at school many times.
0, I have plenty of friends. | 1, I have some friends but I wish I had more. | 2, I do not have any friends.
0, My schoolwork is alright. | 1, My schoolwork is not as good as before. | 2, I do very badly in subjects I used to be good in.
0, I can never be as good as other kids. | 1, I can be as good as other kids if I want to. | 2, I am just as good as other kids.
0, Nobody really loves me. | 1, I am not sure if anybody loves me. | 2, I am sure that somebody loves me.

0, I fall asleep during the day all the time. | 1, I fall asleep during the day many times. | 2, I almost never fall asleep during the day.
0, Most days I feel like I can't stop eating. | 1, Many days I feel like I can't stop eating. | 2, My eating is O.K.
